## CLI Quick Reference

### Session Commands

```bash
# Start/resume session
agentic activate {{ agent_id }}

# Check session status
agentic status
```

### Logging Commands

```bash
# Record a decision
agentic decision --title "Decision Title" --rationale "Why this decision was made"

# Record an assumption
agentic assumption --assumption "Assumption Title" --rationale "Basis for assumption"

# Record feedback
agentic feedback --target "A-01" --severity "medium" --summary "Feedback summary"
```

### Handoff Commands

{% if next_agent_id %}
```bash
# Handoff to next agent
agentic handoff --to {{ next_agent_id }} --artifacts "{{ required_artifacts | join(', ') if required_artifacts else 'artifact1.md, artifact2.md' }}" --notes "Handoff notes"
```
{% else %}
```bash
# End workflow (terminal agent)
agentic end
```
